  "title": "AB03 - Assistant Supervisor – Student Care Centre",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assistant Centre Supervisor</li><li>Monday - Friday 12.30pm to 8pm </li><li>Address: Tampines </li><li>Salary: $2500 - $3000</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Overview:</strong></u><br />As an Assistant Centre Supervisor, you will support the day-to-day operations of the centre and ensure a safe, structured, and nurturing environment for the children. Your responsibilities include, but are not limited to, the following:</p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Oversee the daily care, safety, and well-being of children in the centre</li><li>Fetch children from schools or designated pick-up points</li><li>Coordinate daily tea breaks and arrange lunch with external vendors</li><li>Plan and support holiday programmes and centre activities</li><li>Serve as a key point of contact for management and parents</li><li>Provide guidance on children’s schoolwork and conduct tuition classes when required</li><li>Handle phone calls, walk-in enquiries, and parent communications</li><li>Assist with student registrations, payments, and basic administrative matters</li><li>Maintain general cleanliness and housekeeping standards within the centre</li><li>Support manpower planning and staff coordination</li><li>Carry out any other duties as assigned by management</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements: </strong></u></p><ul><li>Degree/ Diploma/ A levels/ WSQ qualification in Student Care Operations</li><li>Prior tutoring experience</li></ul><p><strong>Remark:</strong></p><ul><li>Shift work is required during school holiday</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
